INSERT INTO `pages` VALUES (1,'Home','Today the web is where your customers are heading but are you ready for them?\r\n\r\nWith over 16 years experience in providing web based solutions I’m confident that we can assist you. In fact every \"service\":/services we offer represents a cost effective way of helping to build your brand online. \r\n\r\nWe specialise in website design and website development, web applications and e-marketing services. We blend our creative, technology and marketing experience to deliver real solutions. \r\n\r\nWe are privately owned, keen to create a positive impact and support the following internet industry associations: AIMIA, IIA and IAB.  \r\n\r\nWould you like to know more? Then why not \"contact us\":contact_us today!     ','website design, web development, websites professional, websites, web applications, e-emarketing, email campaigns, flash banners, ruby on rails, sydney','home','We specialise in website design and website development, web applications and a range of e-marketing services.','','2009-08-24 00:17:02','2010-01-14 00:55:33',NULL,1,'home01.png','image/png',3703,'home02.png','image/png',3710,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,'website design, website development, web applications, e-marketing, sydney',1),(2,'Company','We care about the web and our mission is to try and make the web experience better by delivering the best possible solution. \r\n\r\nThe web is constantly changing the way the world operates. The web has now become a large part of our lives as it\'s entered our offices, homes and even our pockets. With the increasing importance of the web are your current web activities creating a positive brand experience?   \r\n\r\nAll our \"services\":services are delivered by experienced and passionate staff who will help you to plan, manage and implement your solution successfully.\r\n\r\nWe focus and strive to provide the best possible service to medium sized enterprises and corporations. \r\n\r\nDo you need some advice or